{"word":"G5597 - ψώχω - psṓchō - pso'-kho - Rub","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψώχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">psṓchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pso'-kho</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Rub</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிமிட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to rub, rub to pieces"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Prolongation from the same base as <a href=\"#/G5567 - ψάλλω - psállō - psal'-lo/5567\">G5567</a>; to <i>triturate</i>, that is, (by analogy) to <i>rub</i> out (kernels from husks with the fingers or hand): - rub.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}